snippet.title: Meet Amber & Siir Brock 😍 Marriage Boot Camp: Hip Hop Edition
snippet.description:
Amber and Siir Brock have been together for 20 years as friends and lovers, but a trail of infidelity and cheating could put their relationship in jeopardy. Can boot camp change their relationship trajectory?

#HipHopBootCamp #MarriageBootCamp

Four hip hop couples, including rap legend N.O.R.E., face the music at Marriage Boot Camp. Dr. Ish Major & Judge Lynn Toler help them confront lies, tears, and denials, but when dark secrets are exposed, will the relationships survive?
